title: You Promised | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: You Promised | Joel Osteen
description:
God has given us promises of healing, freedom and wholeness in His Word. Stand firm as you wait to see HIs promises come to pass in your life.

 

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
